@crosheaco ‘s Mystery Meat stole my peculiar-loving little heart as soon as I saw it!🧡

I pattern tested this little cutie and it was so much fun! It’s a super quick and easy pattern! Coming soon from @crosheaco ! Give them a follow!

I used @yarnspirations @bernatyarn blanket yarn in ‘terracotta rose’ with a 6.5mm hook. The eyes are 14mm safety eyes. Their cheeky little mouth is embroidered with black medium weight acrylic yarn.
